Text: One of the most sought after Upsetter sides from the late Black Ark period, originally only issued in a small batch, and hopelessly hard to find for years. This excellent dub LP is as dope as all get out, from the kung fu cover image to the spare, funky dubs rolling along on heavy bass, quacking clavinet and earth shaking drums. Seventeen smoking jams
Back to re-up this one, hope you enjoy!
